28
00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:32,280
You two

29
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:33,960
are newlyweds.

30
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:36,160
How can I let you stay with me?

31
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:37,520
Why not?

32
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,319
You see, you don't want

33
