to live with us,

34
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:39,919
which means

35
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:41,520
you must hate one of us.

36
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,879
If it's not me,

37
00:02:43,199 --> 00:02:44,120
it must be him.

38
