Anyway,

39
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,479
we won't push you.

40
00:02:47,479 --> 00:02:48,079
But we can't

41
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:49,160
let you live on your own.

42
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,560
So I'll have to stay with you.

43
00:02:50,799 --> 00:02:51,840
No, Xiaoning,

44
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:52,720
I...

45
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,840
I didn't mean it that way.

46
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:55,199
What I meant was...

47
00:02:55,199 --> 00:02:56,359
That's not what you meant?

48
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,199
Then let's just go home.

49
00:02:58,199 --> 00:02:59,120
It's settled then.

50
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,440
You little rascal,

51
