115
00:05:06,239 --> 00:05:06,960
Her health

116
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:08,080
is improving daily.

117
00:05:08,439 --> 00:05:09,919
This is a chance that fate has given you.

118
00:05:10,559 --> 00:05:12,119
You should seize this opportunity.

119
00:05:12,919 --> 00:05:14,359
Just don't leave yourself with regrets.

120
00:05:17,559 --> 00:05:18,119
Understood.

121
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:22,280
Boss,

122
