128
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:29,919
for less than a month.

129
00:05:30,439 --> 00:05:31,239
There's an element of luck,

130
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,080
but it's mainly thanks to

131
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:33,119
everyone's hard work.

132
00:05:34,479 --> 00:05:36,239
Yuheng, you're being modest.

133
00:05:36,599 --> 00:05:37,320
Everyone knows

134
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:38,679
