143
00:05:56,799 --> 00:05:57,760
Yuheng is right.

144
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,679
I'll be more careful.

145
00:05:59,599 --> 00:06:00,439
Hey, boss,

146
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:02,160
