148
00:06:04,679 --> 00:06:05,280
How about a dinner?

149
00:06:05,999 --> 00:06:07,239
How about tonight!

150
00:06:07,919 --> 00:06:08,359
Tomorrow is the weekend,

151
00:06:08,599 --> 00:06:09,080
