153
00:06:10,559 --> 00:06:11,119
I'll need to head back tonight

154
00:06:11,119 --> 00:06:11,960
to get ready.

155
00:06:12,679 --> 00:06:13,160
How about this:

156
00:06:13,679 --> 00:06:15,160
once the deal is finalized,

157
00:06:15,919 --> 00:06:16,720
I'll take care of the celebration dinner.

158
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:17,559
Sounds good!

159
00:06:17,599 --> 00:06:18,200
It's a deal then.

160
00:06:18,559 --> 00:06:19,239
I'll get back to work now.

161
00:06:19,359 --> 00:06:19,799
Alright.

162
00:06:19,999 --> 00:06:20,679
Let's get to work!

163
00:06:34,599 --> 00:06:35,039
Yuheng.

164
00:06:37,479 --> 00:06:38,160
Yuhui, I've told you before

165
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,039
that in our company...

166
00:06:39,679 --> 00:06:39,999
Mr. Ji.

167
00:06:41,039 --> 00:06:42,479
Sorry I slipped.

168
00:06:42,599 --> 00:06:43,439
I'll be careful next time.

169
00:06:45,799 --> 00:06:46,559
Were you looking for me?

170
00:06:47,479 --> 00:06:48,559
Last time,

171
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:50,119
we went to the hospital to visit your mom.

172
00:06:50,439 --> 00:06:51,280
I asked the staff,

173
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:52,720
and they said that each caregiver

174
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,840
has to take care of two patients.

175
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:55,320
I'm worried that there might

176
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:56,599
not be enough care for your mom.

177
00:06:56,919 --> 00:06:57,720
How about this:

178
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:58,799
I have a friend

179
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:00,559
who runs a nursing home.

180
00:07:01,119 --> 00:07:02,280
Let's hire a caregiver for her.

181
00:07:03,039 --> 00:07:03,880
I can get a discount.

182
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:06,320
The price would be much lower.

183
00:07:06,599 --> 00:07:07,520
I appreciate it,

184
00:07:08,119 --> 00:07:09,679
but she's very happy with the current one.

185
00:07:10,439 --> 00:07:10,999
She doesn't need it.

186
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:11,599
Thanks anyway.

187
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:13,280
Then

188
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:13,999
how about this:

189
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:15,840
Starting today,

190
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:17,679
I'll visit her after work

191
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:19,679
to keep her company.

192
00:07:20,439 --> 00:07:22,439
I actually wanted to go.

193
00:07:22,919 --> 00:07:23,559
But I was

194
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:24,919
worried you might think

195
00:07:24,919 --> 00:07:26,400
I was trying to get close to her

196
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,760
because of work.

197
00:07:28,239 --> 00:07:29,200
I just feel that

198
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,160
she is getting older

199
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:31,119
and quite lonely.

200
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:32,439
You're busy with work,

201
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:33,320
so I can go in your place.

202
00:07:34,119 --> 00:07:35,119
Thank you so much.

203
00:07:35,439 --> 00:07:36,200
But it's really not necessary.

204
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,239
Why not?

205
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,239
I feel I get along

206
00:07:39,239 --> 00:07:40,280
well with her.

207
00:07:40,799 --> 00:07:41,599
And besides,

208
00:07:41,919 --> 00:07:42,679
as a mother,

209
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:45,039
if she sees the right girl

210
00:07:45,359 --> 00:07:46,720
around her son,

211
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:48,479
she should feel more at ease, right?

212
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,479
I've told you already.

213
00:07:53,679 --> 00:07:54,400
It really isn't necessary.

214
00:07:56,679 --> 00:07:57,960
And it's working hours right now.

215
00:07:58,760 --> 00:07:59,439
You should get back to work.

216
00:08:01,799 --> 00:08:02,559
You know very well

217
00:08:02,559 --> 00:08:03,679
how I feel about you.

218
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:14,359
During work hours,

219
00:08:14,359 --> 00:08:15,599
I really shouldn't be saying this.

220
00:08:16,239 --> 00:08:17,799
But to avoid any complications,

221
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,439
I think I should

222
00:08:19,439 --> 00:08:20,320
make things clear.

223
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:22,280
I have someone I like.

224
00:08:23,239 --> 00:08:24,280
[There's no chance for us.]

225
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:25,999
Who is it?

226
00:08:27,439 --> 00:08:27,999
Mr. Ji.

227
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:33,119
I brought the files you requested.

228
00:08:45,799 --> 00:08:46,319
You heard everything?

229
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,280
You were quite firm.

230
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:50,199
Good job.

231
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:52,919
Give it back!

232
00:09:13,439 --> 00:09:14,360
Limin,

233
00:09:15,319 --> 00:09:16,559
Yuheng and I

234
00:09:17,199 --> 00:09:18,199
haven't come to see you

235
00:09:18,199 --> 00:09:19,600
for years.

236
00:09:21,839 --> 00:09:23,600
[I used to come alone,]

237
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:27,079
[and I would always ramble on]

238
00:09:27,319 --> 00:09:29,120
[about him.]

239
00:09:31,199 --> 00:09:32,760
Every time I'd say,

240
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:35,240
next time I'd bring him along.

241
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,799
I've been fooling you all these years.

242
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:41,799
Please don't hold it against me.

243
00:09:45,959 --> 00:09:46,520
[Look,]

244
00:09:47,559 --> 00:09:49,199
I've kept my promise,

245
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,760
and I brought him to see you.

246
00:09:57,839 --> 00:09:58,439
Xiaoning,

247
00:09:59,000 --> 00:09:59,480
come here.

248
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,319
Let dad take a good look at you.

249
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:05,520
Limin,

250
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:09,000
this is our daughter-in-law,

251
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,559
Xiaoning.

252
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:12,760
Xiaoning is

253
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:15,079
not only beautiful but also kind,

254
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,959
a truly wonderful girl.

255
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:19,280
With her by Yuheng's side,

256
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:21,280
we can all feel at ease.

257
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,679
Go on and talk to dad.

258
00:10:37,679 --> 00:10:38,120
I'm good.

259
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:42,319
It's been a while, hasn't it?

260
00:10:49,559 --> 00:10:50,280
Go ahead.

261
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:33,160
I'm doing well.

262
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:37,480
Mom is doing well too.

263
00:11:41,799 --> 00:11:43,360
We'll visit you more often from now on,

264
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,000
dad.

265
00:12:21,679 --> 00:12:22,120
Take it easy.

266
00:12:26,799 --> 00:12:27,719
It's been a long time since I came back.

267
00:12:28,039 --> 00:12:28,679
Let's clean up a bit.

268
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:30,039
We'll manage for tonight.

269
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:46,559
Family photo, mom?

270
00:12:46,799 --> 00:12:47,760
This was taken

271
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:49,799
