285
00:13:24,880 --> 00:13:26,919
He'll definitely prefer the ones you make.

286
00:13:28,160 --> 00:13:29,679
I don't have that kind of confidence.

287
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:31,480
Didn't you just mention?

